ackModal_main_2528031\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gty1665702833951.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gty1665702833951.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gty1665702833951.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gty1665702833951\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n More Properties (Widget Properties)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Add additional properties for the widget that you are defining, and optionally specify the ValRep for the field.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gty1665702833951__p_d9503e1_d9504e1_d9505e1\">Parameters (if any) are initially supplied by Uniface as default parameters for the widget, or are specified in your system initialization file.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gty1665702833951__note_w114ab1b5b3_w115ab1b5_w116ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Most widgets do not have predefined properties that can be set in this dialog. You can use this dialog to add user-defined properties for customized processing.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gty1665702833951__section_lc2_ryk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d608727e57\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gty1665702833951__ul_wc3_ryk_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gty1665702833951__li_d4325e1_d4326e1_d4327e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ruj1665702833669.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ruj1665702833669.html\" title=\"The physical name of the widget property.\">Widget Parameter</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gty1665702833951__li_d4328e1_d4329e1_d4330e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ttk1665702833738.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttk1665702833738.html\" title=\"Specify one or more values for any user-defined or platform-specific properties of a widget or window. Separate multiple values with commas.\">Parameter Value</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gty1665702833951__li_d4331e1_d4332e1_d4333e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmk1665702630446.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmk1665702630446.html\" title=\"This widget supports the ValRep property. For convenience, you can edit the ValRep property of the field in the Widget Properties dialog, even though this is a field-level property rather than a widget property.\">Value and Representation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gty1665702833951__section_rvb_syk_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d608727e96\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gty1665702833951__p_d9512e1_d9513e1_d9514e1\">Click the appropriate <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New</span> or\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span> buttons to add or remove a property or ValRep item.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lov1718340866615.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widget Reference: Forms and Reports</a><p>Widgets in Form components determine the appearance and behavior of fields, labels, occurrences, and entities in components running on Windows.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528031\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528031\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "More Properties (Widget Properties) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 More Properties (Widget Properties) Add additional properties for the widget that you are defining, and optionally specify the ValRep for the field. Parameters (if any) are initially supplied by Uniface as default parameters for the widget, or are specified in your system initialization file. Note: Most widgets do not have predefined properties that can be set in this dialog. You can use this dialog to add user-defined properties for customized processing. Fields Widget Parameter Parameter Value Value and Representation How to Click the appropriate New or Delete buttons to add or remove a property or ValRep item. Related Links Widget Reference: Forms and Reports Widgets in Form components determine the appearance and behavior of fields, labels, occurrences, and entities in components running on Windows. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}